Products.Name: Woolworths Brown Onions
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Woolworths Brown Onions' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
These are the most common onions and are available all year round. 
They are strongly flavoured, firm onions with layers of golden brown paper skins and white flesh. Edible portion includes flesh only. Generally used for cooking rather than eaten raw.

Please note individual onion sizes within the bag may vary.
